TestThrowAttachesData
/ `- throw %a%, %b%` attaches the typed values to the error as a plang list, reachable
/ via %!error.data% inside the handler — full values, not stringified to a single string.
- set %order% = "order-123"
- set %item% = "widget-9"
- throw %order%, %item%, on error set %captured% = %!error.data[1]%
- assert %captured% equals "widget-9"
